data.description: Gorgeous 4-bedroom ranch home, just minutes outside of Logan! Original hardwood flooring throughout main floor with large windows and natural light. This home truly gives a warm and inviting feel.The gorgeous farmhouse kitchen has plenty of cabinetry, stainless steel appliances and vinyl flooring, plus pantry for additional storage. Eat-in space in kitchen with access to attached 1-car garage, and access to full, unfinished basement. Could easily create additional living space, or perfect for more storage! Fenced yard space for kids or pets with mature trees and country views.Newer mechanicals including newer windows, newer furnace/HVAC, updated electrical panel, public water and sewer. Great location on a state route with easy access to all the amenities of Log
